You are here: INSURANCE

Track the financial status of policy terms for claims with the help of the policy term service methods.

InsPolicyTermsService:getCurrentStanding
Use this service to get a list of amounts that represent the current standing of the policy terms associated with a policy or a claim.
InsPolicyTermsService: process
This service retrieves policy terms and calls the policy term's corresponding Attribute Class to process details. For the custom classes, the default method name for the attribute class is - process<Attribute>.
title: Insurance Policy Terms Service
